        <div id="dublin-core-description" class="element">
        <h3>Description</h3>
                    <div class="element-text">RECORD ONE, SIDE ONE:    <br />
Dinah Washington, &quot;The Blues Ain&#039;t Nothing But a Woman Cryin For Her Man&quot;; Cannonball Adderly with Machito and his Orchestra, &quot;Cannonology&quot;; Harry Belafante with Machito and his Orchestra, &quot;Lean on Me&quot;; Herbie Mann with Machito and his Orchestra, &quot;Carabunta&quot;; Steve Allen&#039;s Roundtable All-Stars, &quot;I Thought About You&quot;; Chris Connor and Maynard Ferguson, &quot;I Feel a Song Coming On&quot;.<br />
<br />
RECORD ONE, SIDE TWO:<br />
Louis Armstrong and Duke Ellington, &quot;Cotton Tail&quot;; John Coltrane Quartet, &quot;Exotica&quot;; Dizzy Gillespie, &quot;Paris Swing&quot;; Erroll Garner, &quot;Love for Sale&quot;; Woody Herman Sextet with Nat Adderley, &quot;Lullaby of Birdland&quot;; Charlie Parker &amp; Miles Davis, &quot;Klactoveededstene&quot;<br />
<br />
RECORD TWO, SIDE ONE:<br />
Stan Getz &amp; Horace Silver, &quot;Strike Up the Band&quot;; Art Tatum, &quot;Dark Eyes&quot;; Dizzy Gillespie &amp; Charlie Parker, &quot; Groovin&#039; High&quot;; J. J. Johnson &amp; Kai Winding, &quot;The Shrike&quot;; Bud Powell, &quot;Off Minor&quot;; Joe Newman &amp; Zoot Sims, &quot;Tater Pie&quot;<br />
<br />
RECORD TWO, SIDE TWO:<br />
Joe Williams With Count Basie &amp; His Orchestra, &quot;Everyday&quot;; Sarah Vaughan with Count Basie &amp; His Orchestra, &quot;Until I Met You&quot;; Count Basie &amp; His Orchestra, &quot;Tickle Toe&quot;; Joe Williams with Lambert, Hendricks &amp; Ross with Count Basie &amp; His Orchestra, &quot;Going to Chicago Blues&quot;; Billy Eckstine with Count Basie &amp; his Orchestra, &quot;Jelly, Jelly&quot;; Tony Bennett with count Basie &amp; his Orchestra, &quot;I Guess I&#039;ll Have to Change My Plans&quot;<br />
</div>
